            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
            <h4 class="wcuheader">Collaboration that Scales</h4>
            <div class="wcutext">
                DevOps is as much about people as it is about technology. Using Git and Azure DevOps Boards, I experienced firsthand how collaboration tools help teams stay aligned, track progress, and resolve issues efficiently. These practices reinforced the importance of communication, version control, and teamwork in professional development environments.
            </div>
        </div>
